articles.title: The four US Supreme Court cases to watch - BBC.com
articles.description: The top US court is back in session with cases that may affect American life - and its standing in the public.
articles.content:
A new nine-month term begins for the US Supreme Court on Monday with major cases that will shape many aspects of American life.
The court's nine justices are back after last year's blockbuster term,… [+5994 chars]
